      "content": "Yes! Watched \"KGF 2\". Very good action. You?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "I loved KGF 2 too! The action scenes are amazing. Do you enjoy wrestling as much as the movies?"
    },
    {
