      "content": "Good, tired but happy. Like victory feeling. Sometimes lose, but still good."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You sound very positive! Losing can teach a lot. What do you do when you feel tired after practice?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Eat banana, rest. Or have small kannavu (tea). Simple things."
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "That sounds perfect! Tea helps me relax too. Did you try any new moves in wrestling lately?"
    }
